flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Get User Input: Base IP]
    B --> C[Get User Input: Subnet Mask]
    C --> D[Calculate IP Range]
    D --> E[Loop through IP Range]
    E --> F[Format IP Address]
    F --> G[Spawn Blocking Thread]
    G --> H[Create Channel]
    H --> I[Execute Ping]
    I --> J{Check Result}
    J -->|Success| K[Print Host is Up]
    J -->|Failure| L[Print Host is Unreachable]
    K --> M{More IPs?}
    L --> M
    M -->|Yes| E
    M -->|No| N[End]
